Vinn14  m0_inn14  0  DC 0.8
Vinp15  m0_inp15  0  DC 0.8
Vinn15  m0_inn15  0  DC 0.8
Vinp16  m0_inp16  0  DC 0.8
Vinn16  m0_inn16  0  DC 0.8
Vinp17  m0_inp17  0  DC 0.8
Vinn17  m0_inn17  0  DC 0.8
