Vinn24  m0_inn24  0  DC 0.8
Vinp25  m0_inp25  0  DC 0.8
Vinn25  m0_inn25  0  DC 0.8
Vinp26  m0_inp26  0  DC 0.8
Vinn26  m0_inn26  0  DC 0.8
Vinp27  m0_inp27  0  DC 0.8
Vinn27  m0_inn27  0  DC 0.8
