Vinn28  m0_inn28  0  DC 0.8
Vinp29  m0_inp29  0  DC 0.8
Vinn29  m0_inn29  0  DC 0.8
Vinp30  m0_inp30  0  DC 0.8
Vinn30  m0_inn30  0  DC 0.8
Vinp31  m0_inp31  0  DC 0.8
Vinn31  m0_inn31  0  DC 0.8

* ── WE_route: repeating 5ns pulses every 50ns (fires at t=50,100,150... ns) ─
Vwe_route  we_route  0  PULSE(0 1.8 50n 1n 1n 5n 50n)

