* ── Routing weight pre-initialization ────────────────────────────────────────
* vw_route_0_0=0.75V → XMPRED_r_0_0 (W=4/L=0.35) sinks ~28µA from i_pred_0
* This exceeds prediction sources (~10.7µA) → V(i_pred_0) drops → ierr_dig_0=HIGH
* WE_route pulse fires Hebbian: v_pre=sf_out_0≈1.14V (PMOS SF §71; was 0.29V with NMOS SF)
* LTD decreases vw_route_0_0 — correct adaptive response (suppresses over-prediction)
.ic V(xlink.vw_route_0_0)=0.75

